  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Problem\r\n\r\nIf start recording an audio message and switch to the keyboard while recording, and then open the audio message panel again, the button of the recording will not have an outer circle.\r\nThe issue isn't reproducible every time.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\n![ezgif com-resize (19)](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/67952253/93358199-7bb14800-f841-11ea-94b2-01970236bfaf.gif)\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open chat\r\n- Tap the audio message icon on the input field \r\n- Start to record audio\r\n- Switch to the keyboard without tapping stop (tap text input or keyboard icon)\r\n- Tap audio message icon again\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: Nightly 16/09\r\n- Operating System: Android 10, iOS 14\r\n",
